            <div class="card-content">

              <h3 class="header">
                Our Mission
              </h3>

              <p class="flow-text">
                FORGED is focused on using our skills and talents to enhance the world around us.
                We hope that by providing context for data used by key decision makers, we can facilitate community betterment.
              </p>

