                The FORGED Commitment
              </h4>

              <p class="flow-text">
                The foundation of FORGED Development is based on our belief that putting in an honest day of hard work starts and ends with our commitment to deliver consistency in our products and customer service each and everyday.
                The teams at FORGED are experienced professionals focused on providing the tools needed to contribute in the success of our clients. We create software that helps various industries sort through their collected data and assist them in creating a relevant, precise informational picture that can be used to impact the organization’s effectiveness.

                <blockquote>
                  It is our commitment to actively listen, learn, and understand our clients’ needs.
                </blockquote>
              </p>

              <h4 class="header">
                FORGED Alliance™
              </h4>

              <p class="flow-text">
                The FORGED Alliance™ is a program for the introduction of new software applications to our existing clients prior to commercial release.
                This is part of our ongoing collaborative relationship we have with our clients to ensure that we are developing tools that will be useful in their day-to-day business environment.
                As a member of the Alliance you will also receive quarterly webinar trainings, access to the bi-annual Director call, and can participate in determining features for future software application releases.
              </p>

